Class JobList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<Object,Object>

    public class JobList
extends Properties
    Helper class that encapsulates storage and retrieval of upload jobs to persistent storage. Data is stored in an external directory outside the application's private space so that it is retained across installs.
